bit counter-intuitive

00:01:01.929 --> 00:01:03.003
for a lot of ya'll,

00:01:03.003 --> 00:01:04.241
especially with math backgrounds,

00:01:04.241 --> 00:01:06.237
in fact, it's a little
bit uncomfortable for me,

00:01:06.237 --> 00:01:09.777
we often prefer to put time
on the horizontal axis,

00:01:09.777 --> 00:01:12.803
and position on the vertical axis,

00:01:12.803 --> 00:01:14.775
so this is a little bit counter-intuitive.

00:01:14.775 --> 00:01:15.933
But this is,

00:01:15.933 --> 00:01:18.188
you know, our choice is
a little bit arbitrary,

00:01:18.188 --> 00:01:20.646
